6_SAS_On CapEx Vs OpEx


Q1
Most important thing when it comes to building an application/starting a business is capital (Money)? True/False
ANS
TRUE - IN THE PREVIOUS DECADE THIS WAS TRUE, BUT NOWADAYS THERE ARE OTHER OPTIONS.
Q2
What would small and large businesses have to purchase if they want to grow their business?
ANS
DATA CENTERS, SERVERS - BUILD NEW SERVICES TO DELIVER TO CUSTOMERS.

(R&D, TECHNOLOGY & INFRA)

CAPEX

OPEX - NO NEED TO INCUR UP FRONT COSTS, PAY AS YOU GO
